in our everyday lives.

00:02:06.610 --> 00:02:08.699 align:middle line:90%
There's a tendency to do that.

00:02:08.699 --> 00:02:10.870 align:middle line:84%
And there has been a
reluctance in the mainstream.

00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:13.482 align:middle line:84%
