in the mainstream media

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:24.270 align:middle line:84%
to share the facts of
what this new normal is.

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:25.540 align:middle line:90%
And I want to be very clear.

00:02:25.540 --> 00:02:28.210 align:middle line:84%
It's not about making anyone
wrong or making anyone right.

00:02:28.210 --> 00:02:31.660 align:middle line:84%
