00:02:31.660 --> 00:02:33.160 align:middle line:84%
We are living in a
time of extremes.

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.534 align:middle line:84%
How can we deal
with the extremes

00:02:34.534 --> 00:02:38.100 align:middle line:84%
